## â–¶ï¸ How It Works
1. A button click triggers the display of vowels :contentReference[oaicite:0]{index=0}
2. The vowels are stored in an array: `["a", "e", "i", "o", "u", "y"]`
3. Each vowel is displayed inside a styled card
4. CSS animations enhance the visual appearance :contentReference[oaicite:1]{index=1}

